m of copium is to laugh at the madness and  embrace the journey.<\/p><p>And let’s be real—you deserve a break from fumbling through another Dr.  Seuss word salad. No more stumbling through Fox in Socks at bedtime—this one’s got layers of crypto humor baked in, so you’ll actually enjoy  reading it (even if your little degen descendant doesn’t get the jokes… yet).<\/p>","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_font":"body","secondary_color":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"button_R7REUV":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","button_size":"md","button_external":false,"button_icon":true}}},"block_order":["heading_XmqNjr","text_fKEcxR","button_R7REUV"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"text_alignment":"left","text_alignment_mobile":"left","heading":"","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_width":"small","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","color_text":"#171717","color_background":"#dc3fb1","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":100,"divider":false,"narrow":true,"rounded":false}},"newsletter_8XcrGk":{"type":"newsletter","blocks":{"heading_pTfExM":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Sign up and save","heading_size":"title-lg tracking-heading","heading_tag":"h2","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_44niw3":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Be the first to know when we launch.<\/p>","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_font":"body","secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"form_4DJjEL":{"type":"form","settings":{}}},"block_order":["heading_pTfExM","text_44niw3","form_4DJjEL"],"settings":{"content_width":"medium","text_alignment":"left","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":false,"narrow":true,"rounded":false}},"images_with_text_M8eG6c":{"type":"images-with-text","blocks":{"heading_qeTmJK":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"About Us","heading_size":"title-md","heading_tag":"h2","highlighted_text":"text","highlighted_scribble":"squiggle-underline-2"}},"text_kWtXbQ":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Just a degen who got tired of low-effort, cringe-worthy crypto merch. So I made my own. Clean, high-quality, and actually wearable crypto drip.  At first, it was just for me, but now it’s time to share it with the  community.<br\/><br\/>As for the book? I’ve been through more cycles than I’d like to admit.  Sometimes, the best form of copium is to laugh at the madness and  embrace the journey.<\/p><p>And let’s be real—you deserve a break from fumbling through another Dr.  Seuss word salad. No more stumbling through Fox in Socks at bedtime—this one’s got layers of crypto humor baked in, so you’ll actually enjoy  reading it (even if your little degen descendant doesn’t get the jokes… yet).<\/p>","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_font":"body","secondary_color":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["heading_qeTmJK","text_kWtXbQ"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GM_mascot_2.png","image_ratio":"landscape","image_width":"small","layout":"image_first","text_alignment":"left","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"#fafafa","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":true,"full_width":false,"rounded":true,"enable_parallax":true}},"faq_yDEybi":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"question_nWGGNG":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Loaded up my bags—will it all arrive at the same time?","text":"<p>Akin to the Bitcoin blockchain, our supply chain is <br\/>decentralized—no single point of failure here, just the best quality at <br\/>the best price.<\/p><p>This means your goodies might hit your address (postal, not crypto, you degen!) at different times.<\/p><p>Most products are minted just for you the moment you order.<br\/> That might mean waiting a few extra block confirmations before they <br\/>reach your doorstep, but trust us—it’ll be worth the wait!<br\/><br\/><\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_HxPzkp":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Cool drip, but it seems expensive. What's the deal?","text":"<p>Think bitcoin, not sh*tcoin—No fast fashion rugs here.<\/p><p>Significant time, care, and thought has gone into the design of these products, so it makes sense to print them on gear that actually lasts. Get ready to HODL these long-term.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_e4MncW":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Fiat is for losers. Can I pay with crypto?","text":"<p>Sooooooon! This is on our roadmap.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_jcRpjV":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Wen whitepaper? What are the tokenomics?","text":"<p>Fren, get out of the trenches. No TGEs, CAs or tokemonics here—just degenerative merch and a kids book that slaps. Buy hey, feel free to ape into a pair of Shoetoshi Nakamotes.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"contact_7bAYEz":{"type":"contact","settings":{"heading":"Didn’t find your answer?","text":"<p>Don't hestitate to contact us<\/p>","show_phone":false,"avatar_height":60,"highlighted_text":"no